name: Sky Farm (cmcgdd)
description:
Sky Farm is a snake-inspired farming simulator. This build represents an early Alpha version and may contain bugs.

What's New???

  • UI/UX Improvements
  • Removed potato and tomato seed packets in preparation for pending "Market" update.

Known Bugs

  • None for now!

If you've got some time, I'd love to hear your feedback! Development is still in the very early stages, so I'm still looking for very general feedback. Anything you have to say is what I want to know!
